      • getLabel

        public static SyntaxTree getLabel(Expression setExpression)
        Returns the label of the syntactic tree representing the set. This is a symbol with the value of one of IntensionalSet.MULTI_SET_LABEL, IntensionalSet.UNI_SET_LABEL, ExtensionalSets.MULTI_SET_LABEL, or ExtensionalSets.UNI_SET_LABEL.

      • expandApplicationOfAssociativeCommutativeFunction

        public static Expression expandApplicationOfAssociativeCommutativeFunction(Expression functionApplicationOnIntensionalSet)
        Transforms an application of a associative commutative function to an intensional set with one or more indices to an equivalent expression in which intensional sets have a single index each. An example is sum( {{ (on X in 1..10, Y in 1..10) 3 | X != Y }} ) being transformed to sum( {{ (on X in 1..10) sum({{ (on Y in 1..10) 3 | X != Y }}) | true }} )
        Parameters:
        functionApplicationOnIntensionalSet -
        Returns:
